HTML-CTPP2 version 2.5.9
========================

HTML::CTPP2 - Perl interface for CTPP2 library

This module is very similar to well-known Sam Tregar's HTML::Template but works
in 22 - 25 times faster and provides extra functionality.
CTPP2 template language dialect contains 11 operators: <TMPL_var>, <TMPL_if>,
<TMPL_elsif>, <TMPL_else>, <TMPL_unless>, <TMPL_loop>, <TMPL_udf>, <TMPL_include>,
<TMPL_comment>, <TMPL_call> and <TMPL_block>.


INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires installed CTPP2 library version 2.4.1 or higher.
You can download it here: http://ctpp.havoc.ru/download/
To install CTPP2 library type the following:

   wget http://ctpp.havoc.ru/download/ctpp2-2.X.X.tar.gz
   gunzip ctpp2-2.X.X.tar.gz
   tar -xf ctpp2-2.X.X.tar
   cd ctpp2-2.X.X
   cmake .
   make
   make test
   make install

Since CTPP uses cmake you should have installed cmake building system,
see http://www.cmake.org/


